<p>Yup, Magnolia is a killer.  But, the rewards are spectacular.  I think it's got some of the best terrain and views of our lunchtime forays.  I'll definitely head back up sometime this summer, perhaps as part of a big loop on the Peak-to-Peak.</p>
<p>Anyhow, Dave hit the creek on the way down.  Needed to bring his core temperature back down to 104&deg;F.  You okay, Underwood?</p>
